    "title": {
      "rendered": "How To Integrate Social Media Into Your Nonprofit&#8217;s Online Contests"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/online-contests-graphics.jpg\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-14563\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"online-contests-graphics\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/online-contests-graphics-300x300.jpg?resize=300%2C300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/online-contests-graphics.jpg?resize=300%2C300&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/online-contests-graphics.jpg?resize=150%2C150&amp;ssl=1 150w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/online-contests-graphics.jpg?resize=200%2C200&amp;ssl=1 200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/online-contests-graphics.jpg?resize=75%2C75&amp;ssl=1 75w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/online-contests-graphics.jpg?w=449&amp;ssl=1 449w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /></a>The <a href=\"http://www.awf.org/safari-sweepstakes/\">African Wildlife Foundation&#8217;s Annual Safari\u00a0Sweepstakes</a> promotion is as close as it gets to perfect. The design and branding is modern and <a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/2013/04/07/nonprofitresponsivedesign/\">mobile-optimized</a>, visuals and call-to-action graphics are prioritized over text, and social media is integrated throughout the entire process of entering the sweepstakes. Not only <a href=\"http://www.awf.org/safari-sweepstakes/\">by entering the contest</a> may you win a trip of a lifetime, but by entering you can also study how the contest promotion and entry process can be applied to your own nonprofit&#8217;s contest promotions and email fundraising campaigns.</p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">1. Contest Announcement via Email</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong></strong><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&#8211; Large photo and &#8220;Enter Now&#8221; button in the email header.<br />\n</span>&#8211; Another large &#8220;Enter Now&#8221; button in the body of the email.<br />\n&#8211; Social network sharing functionality.<br />\n&#8211; &#8220;Donate Now&#8221; and charity rating buttons in the email footer.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-1.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14466 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"AWF Contest Email 1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-1.png?resize=600%2C332\" width=\"600\" height=\"332\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-1.png?resize=300%2C166&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14551\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"AWF\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF.png?resize=600%2C282\" width=\"600\" height=\"282\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF.png?resize=300%2C141&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-3.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"size-full wp-image-14468 aligncenter\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"AWF Contest Email 3\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-3.png?resize=600%2C291\" width=\"600\" height=\"291\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-3.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-3.png?resize=300%2C145&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /><br />\n</a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>2. The Contest Entry Process<br />\n</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8211; Large photo and &#8220;Enter Now&#8221; button on the contest entry page.<br />\n&#8211; Email a friend pitch on the contest entry confirmation landing page.<br />\n&#8211; Social network sharing functionality on the contest entry confirmation landing page.<br />\n&#8211; &#8220;Donate&#8221; button on the contest entry confirmation landing page.<br />\n&#8211; Social network icons on the contest entry confirmation landing page.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/conest1.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14471\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"conest1\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/conest1.png?resize=600%2C480\" width=\"600\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/conest1.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/conest1.png?resize=300%2C240&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Entry Confirmation Landing Page:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-22.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14555\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Contest-2\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-22.png?resize=600%2C217\" width=\"600\" height=\"217\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-22.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-22.png?resize=300%2C108&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Entry Confirmation Email:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-3.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14474\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"Contest 3\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-3.png?resize=600%2C464\" width=\"600\" height=\"464\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-3.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/Contest-3.png?resize=300%2C232&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n3. Contest Entry Confirmation Email</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n</strong>&#8211; Large &#8220;Thank You&#8221; photo\u00a0in email header.<br />\n&#8211; Social network sharing functionality\u00a0in the body of the email.<br />\n&#8211; Social network icons in the body of the email.<br />\n&#8211; Donation pitch\u00a0in the body of the email.<br />\n&#8211; Social network icons again in the footer of the email.<br />\n&#8211; &#8220;Donate Now&#8221; and charity rating buttons in email footer.<strong><br />\n</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-4.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14476\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"AWF Contest Email 4\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-4.png?resize=600%2C384\" width=\"600\" height=\"384\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-4.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-4.png?resize=300%2C192&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-5.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter  wp-image-14478\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"AWF Contest Email 5\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-5.png?resize=600%2C427\" width=\"600\" height=\"427\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-5.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-5.png?resize=300%2C213&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-6.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14479\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"AWF Contest Email 6\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-6.png?resize=600%2C421\" width=\"600\" height=\"421\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-6.png?w=600&amp;ssl=1 600w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Email-6.png?resize=300%2C210&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><br />\n4. Contest Announcement Image for Social Networks</strong></h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Entry-Image.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14558\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"AWF Contest Entry Image\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Entry-Image.png?resize=449%2C267\" width=\"449\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Entry-Image.png?w=449&amp;ssl=1 449w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/AWF-Contest-Entry-Image.png?resize=300%2C178&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 449px) 100vw, 449px\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Shared on Facebook:</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/facebook-awf.png\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-14575\" style=\"border: 1px solid black;\" alt=\"facebook awf\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/facebook-awf.png?resize=449%2C435\" width=\"449\" height=\"435\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/facebook-awf.png?w=449&amp;ssl=1 449w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/facebook-awf.png?resize=300%2C290&amp;ssl=1 300w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 449px) 100vw, 449px\" /></a></p>\n",
